  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClassRegistry
    Defines interface for class registries.
    NameFactory
    Interface for class that provides name for method parameters.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractClassFactory
    Defines a factory for creating skeleton implementations of the abstract methods of Abstract Java classes.
    DefaultNameFactory
    Defines a default parameter name factory for the InterfaceFactory.
    DelegateFactory
    Defines a factory for generating methods that delegate tasks to be performed by an instance of one class (the delegator) to an instance of another class (the delegee.
    EventSourceFactory  
    ImportWizard
    Converts an unqualified class name to import statements by scanning through the classpath.
    InterfaceFactory
    Defines a factory for creating skeleton implementations of Java interfaces.
    MethodFactory
    Defines a factory for creating skeleton implementations of Java interfaces.
    MethodOverrideFactory
    Defines a factory for creating an override of a method defined in a superclass.
    Signature
    Defines a method signature.
    SignatureContainer
    A container for method signatures.
